## gf_two_blobs

## Description
Two densely connected blobs (vertices 0->n-1 and n->2n-1)   connected by a single edge (0->n). 


## Usage
```r
gf_two_blobs(sc, blob_size) 
```

## Arguments
|Arguments|Description|
|---|---|
| sc | A Spark connection. |
| blob_size | The size of each blob. |





## Examples

::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
library(graphframes)
gf_two_blobs(sc, 3) 
```
:::
